<pre><code>#include &lt;iostream&gt;  int main() {     int a = 999999999999999999;     std::cout &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt; std::endl;     std::cout &lt;&lt; 999999999999999999 &lt;&lt; std::endl;     return 0; } </code></pre>  <p>The output of above program is <code>-1486618625</code> and  <code>999999999999999999</code>.</p>  <p>In both the <code>cout</code> we are giving the same number, so why are the outputs different?</p>  <p>Also are <code>long long int a=999999999999999</code> same as <code>int a=9999999999999999ll</code>?</p>